  "description": "MariaDB/BigQuery/Oracle hybrid with rows_unbounded_to_unbounded window default, EXTRACT temporal syntax, double-quoted identifiers preserving case, set-op default ALL, and LIMIT/OFFSET row limiting with CONCAT_WS-flavored concat.",
